    "as 'long s') or 'r' are distinguished.",
    "Machine learning-based models are indifferent to character sets, however, their capabilities are confined to the scope of their training data.",
    "From a legal perspective and because of the data's value due to its laborious production, Ground Truth should at least be understood as data (by)product of a project and considered for publication.",
